Commentary Text: Shami to Rahul, out Caught by Wade!! Unplayable! Simply unplayable. Fullish around off, brings Rahul half-forward, he has the bat close to the pad in trying to defend, the bat hits the pad, but the ball takes the outside-edge of the bat as well, at the same time. Rahul c Wade b Shami 0(1)

Commentary Text: Chameera to Shankar, out Bowled!! Absolute peach from Chameera. The inswinging yorker and Shankar, with his tall stature and high back lift, couldn't get his bat down in time. Tries to squeeze it but too late and ends up losing balance as he tip-toes into the off-side whilst his stumps take the beating. This is high quality pace bowling from the Sri Lankan and the ideal start for the Giants. Shankar b Chameera 4(6)
